name: FPC  Unexpected unlockable
description:
First of the eight limited crypto artwork experiences from the "Future Perfect Continuous" collection. 

The zeitgeist of this artwork experience narrates extreme fiat currency devaluation. 
Homeless boomer leans for a slice of rusty pizza through the waste bin full of banknotes. 
Everybody is throwing them away. 
Cold pizza, even with a pineapple on it, has more value. 
It can be eaten at least (of course, after you throw away all pineapples).
